	<entry>
		<title>Opções de Extensões para Vídeos no Joomla</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://backup/portal/joomla-3/extensoes/opcoes-de-extensoes-para-videos-no-joomla.html"/>
		<published>2017-08-28T14:24:02-03:00</published>
		<updated>2017-08-28T14:24:02-03:00</updated>
		<id>http://backup/portal/joomla-3/extensoes/opcoes-de-extensoes-para-videos-no-joomla.html</id>
		<author>
			<name>Ribamar FS</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h4&gt;Opções de Extensões para Vídeos no Joomla&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All Videos&lt;/strong&gt; - adiciona vídeos em artigos&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.joomlaworks.net/extensions/free/allvideos&quot;&gt;http://www.joomlaworks.net/extensions/free/allvideos&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Configurar o AllVideos (diretórios e dimensões)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Local Video Folder = images/stories/videos&lt;br /&gt;Local Audio Folder = images/audio&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Basta enviar o vídeo para a pasta /video e áudio para a pasta /audio (ambas no raiz do site) e inserir a tag (como abaixo) no artigo, como abaixo&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;{youtube}heu37ej3qs{/youtube}, {flv}batman_darknight{/flv} or {mp3}pixies_bonemachine{/mp3} {swfremote}/videos/foo.swf{/swfremote}&lt;br /&gt;compatible video and audio formats like flv, swf, mov, mp4, wmv, wma, mp3, 3gp, webm, ogv, ogg, divx and more.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suportados&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;youtube, vimeo e nuitos outros&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;YouTube video with 600x450 dimensions that autoplays on page load&lt;br /&gt;{youtube}he73js822|600|450|1{/youtube}&lt;br /&gt;MP4 (H.264 Video)    images/stories/videos/our-family-trips/paris.mp4    {mp4}our-family-trips/paris{/mp4}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;FLV    images/stories/videos/our-family-trips/paris.flv    {flv}our-family-trips/paris{/flv}&lt;br /&gt;FLV hosted on remote server    http://domain.com/media/paris.flv    {flvremote}http://domain.com/media/paris.flv{/flvremote}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;OGV (OGG VIdeo)    images/stories/videos/our-family-trips/paris.ogv    {ogv}our-family-trips/paris{/ogv}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;SWF (Shockwave Flash)    images/stories/videos/banners/promo.swf    {swf}banners/promo{/swf}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Áudio&lt;br /&gt;MP3    images/stories/audio/podcasts/theJoomlaShow.mp3    {mp3}podcasts/theJoomlaShow{/mp3}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mais informações&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.joomlaworks.net/support/docs/allvideos&quot;&gt;http://www.joomlaworks.net/support/docs/allvideos&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outras Alternativas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Video Gallery - Plugin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://huge-it.com/joomla-video-gallery/&quot;&gt;https://huge-it.com/joomla-video-gallery/&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Usos: vídeo em popup em artigo, vídeo slider em artigo, Lightbox Video Gallery, Video Slider e Thumbnails View&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yendif Video Share - Componente&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-download.html&quot;&gt;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-download.html&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-overview.html&quot;&gt;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-overview.html&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla/&quot;&gt;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla/&lt;/a&gt;  - demo &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Joombig video slider vertical - Módulo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://joombig.com/download-extension-free/407-down-joombig-video-slider-vertical&quot;&gt;http://joombig.com/download-extension-free/407-down-joombig-video-slider-vertical&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://joombig.com/extensions-detail/442-joombig-video-slider-vertical&quot;&gt;http://joombig.com/extensions-detail/442-joombig-video-slider-vertical&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://joombig.com/demo-extensions1/index.php/demo/joombig-video-slider-vertical&quot;&gt;http://joombig.com/demo-extensions1/index.php/demo/joombig-video-slider-vertical&lt;/a&gt;  - demo &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h4&gt;Opções de Extensões para Vídeos no Joomla&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All Videos&lt;/strong&gt; - adiciona vídeos em artigos&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.joomlaworks.net/extensions/free/allvideos&quot;&gt;http://www.joomlaworks.net/extensions/free/allvideos&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Configurar o AllVideos (diretórios e dimensões)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Local Video Folder = images/stories/videos&lt;br /&gt;Local Audio Folder = images/audio&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Basta enviar o vídeo para a pasta /video e áudio para a pasta /audio (ambas no raiz do site) e inserir a tag (como abaixo) no artigo, como abaixo&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;{youtube}heu37ej3qs{/youtube}, {flv}batman_darknight{/flv} or {mp3}pixies_bonemachine{/mp3} {swfremote}/videos/foo.swf{/swfremote}&lt;br /&gt;compatible video and audio formats like flv, swf, mov, mp4, wmv, wma, mp3, 3gp, webm, ogv, ogg, divx and more.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suportados&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;youtube, vimeo e nuitos outros&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;YouTube video with 600x450 dimensions that autoplays on page load&lt;br /&gt;{youtube}he73js822|600|450|1{/youtube}&lt;br /&gt;MP4 (H.264 Video)    images/stories/videos/our-family-trips/paris.mp4    {mp4}our-family-trips/paris{/mp4}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;FLV    images/stories/videos/our-family-trips/paris.flv    {flv}our-family-trips/paris{/flv}&lt;br /&gt;FLV hosted on remote server    http://domain.com/media/paris.flv    {flvremote}http://domain.com/media/paris.flv{/flvremote}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;OGV (OGG VIdeo)    images/stories/videos/our-family-trips/paris.ogv    {ogv}our-family-trips/paris{/ogv}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;SWF (Shockwave Flash)    images/stories/videos/banners/promo.swf    {swf}banners/promo{/swf}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Áudio&lt;br /&gt;MP3    images/stories/audio/podcasts/theJoomlaShow.mp3    {mp3}podcasts/theJoomlaShow{/mp3}&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mais informações&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.joomlaworks.net/support/docs/allvideos&quot;&gt;http://www.joomlaworks.net/support/docs/allvideos&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outras Alternativas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Video Gallery - Plugin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://huge-it.com/joomla-video-gallery/&quot;&gt;https://huge-it.com/joomla-video-gallery/&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Usos: vídeo em popup em artigo, vídeo slider em artigo, Lightbox Video Gallery, Video Slider e Thumbnails View&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yendif Video Share - Componente&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-download.html&quot;&gt;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-download.html&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-overview.html&quot;&gt;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla-video-share-overview.html&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla/&quot;&gt;https://yendifplayer.com/joomla/&lt;/a&gt;  - demo &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Joombig video slider vertical - Módulo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://joombig.com/download-extension-free/407-down-joombig-video-slider-vertical&quot;&gt;http://joombig.com/download-extension-free/407-down-joombig-video-slider-vertical&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://joombig.com/extensions-detail/442-joombig-video-slider-vertical&quot;&gt;http://joombig.com/extensions-detail/442-joombig-video-slider-vertical&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://joombig.com/demo-extensions1/index.php/demo/joombig-video-slider-vertical&quot;&gt;http://joombig.com/demo-extensions1/index.php/demo/joombig-video-slider-vertical&lt;/a&gt;  - demo &lt;/p&gt;</content>
